description: The Health Nut On Wheels is a truck serving healthy, real food to the streets of Miami. This food is free of pesticides, antibiotics, steroids, cages & industrial feeding lots, and the menu is primarily based on paleo  nutrition. Just one day's offerings can include Cuban-style Boliche, homemade tuna salad with local mango salad, flattened chicken breast, and meatloaf. Don't miss out on one of these fantastic meals!
name: The Health Nut On Wheels
